name: INIntentResolutionResult
desc: A resolution result for a parameter of an intent object.

items.name: class func needsValue() -> Self
items.desc: Creates an object whose resolution indicates that a required parameter value is missing.

items.name: class func notRequired() -> Self
items.desc: Creates an object whose resolution indicates that you don’t need the value of the parameter.

items.name: class func unsupported() -> Self
items.desc: Creates an object whose resolution indicates that your app doesn’t support the specified value.
